        "TileImage": "$($repository 4cc95d65-18a0-4424-b805-7fdf863dfedb).Image",
        "Description": "Hello Agents,\r\rI am happy to announce your spring PTO was approved and the ICA will pay for a full time vacation in the maldives as a bonus for outstanding service.\rHaven Island is a beautiful place to relax, dip your toes in the water or have some Bahama Mamas.\rAlso while you&apos;re already there, we approved some targets for elimination.\rWhat? Don&apos;t look at me like that. It&apos;s optional.\rJust know it will affect you yearly performance review.\r\rGood killing agents,\rCelllie",
